# ğŸŒ Sun-Kissed & Southern â€” Backend API

[![ğŸš€ Live Backend (Render)](https://img.shields.io/badge/Backend-Live--API-4e4e4e?style=for-the-badge&logo=flask&logoColor=white)](https://sun-kissed-backend.onrender.com)

This is the **Flask-based backend** powering [Sun-Kissed & Southern](https://sun-kissed-and-southern.netlify.app), a modern e-commerce platform for Florida beach-inspired apparel. It includes full support for authentication, order management, discounts, returns, and admin dashboards.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ” JWT authentication + role-based access (`admin`, `user`, `fulfillment`, `customer_service`)
- ğŸ‘• Product, variant, and inventory management
- ğŸ›’ Full checkout + coupon logic (Cardknox sandbox mode)
- ğŸ” Returns and refunds (w/ optional restock)
- ğŸ’¬ Product reviews (with moderation)
- ğŸ’– Favorites system
- ğŸ“Š Admin analytics: low stock, top customers, revenue
- ğŸ“š Lifestyle blog with optional weather widget

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- Python 3.12 + Flask (REST API)
- PostgreSQL + SQLAlchemy ORM
- JWT via `flask-jwt-extended`
- Alembic + Flask-Migrate
- Pytest for testing
- Deployed via **Render**
